Command/setting sigs

Unofficial ConTeXt Wiki mirror

Last modified: 2025-01-18

The idea here is to be able to tell how setting signatures change from command to command.

This table was generated from the context-en.xml interface file from the ConTeXt distribution, retrieved 2020-05-29 from the context-mirror repository on GitHub.
